'''[[印度|印度]]的[[咖啡|咖啡]]產業'''目前由[[印度南部|印度南部]]佔主導地位，[[卡納塔克邦|卡納塔克邦]]、[[喀拉拉邦|喀拉拉邦]]和[[泰米爾納德邦|泰米爾納德邦]]的咖啡產量合共佔全國超過90%<ref name=value>{{Cite web|url=http://ip.cals.cornell.edu/courses/iard602/2006spring/documents/sample_papers/value_coffee.ppt#1|title=Value Addition to Coffee in India|accessdate=2010-10-05|publisher=Cornell Education:Intag 602|first=Salomey|last=Yeboah|date=8 March 2005|archive-date=2006-09-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060919130235/http://ip.cals.cornell.edu/courses/iard602/2006spring/documents/sample_papers/value_coffee.ppt#1|dead-url=no}}</ref>；目前印度全國大約有25萬人栽種[[咖啡豆|咖啡豆]]<ref name="Lee">{{cite book|url=http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=BuwFF2JLw1MC&pg=PA293|last1=Lee|first1=Hau Leung|last2=Lee|first2=Chung-Yee|title=Building supply chain excellence in emerging economies|year=2007|pages=293–94|isbn=0-387-38428-6|access-date=2014-07-08|archive-date=2012-11-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121113110037/http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=BuwFF2JLw1MC&pg=PA293|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而全國幾乎80％的咖啡產量<ref name="Illy & Viani">{{cite book|last1=Illy|first1=Andrea|last2=Viani|first2=Rinantonio|title=Espresso coffee: the science of quality|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=AJdlfSFCmVIC&pg=PA47|year=2005|publisher=Academic Press|isbn=0-12-370371-9|page=47|access-date=2014-07-08|archive-date=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140708113219/http://books.google.com/books?id=AJdlfSFCmVIC&pg=PA47|dead-url=no}}</ref>會出口到[[德國|德國]]、[[俄羅斯|俄羅斯]]、[[西班牙|西班牙]]、[[比利時|比利時]]、[[斯洛文尼亞|斯洛文尼亞]]、[[美國|美國]]、[[日本|日本]]、[[希臘|希臘]]、[[荷蘭|荷蘭]]、[[法國|法國]]、[[意大利|意大利]]等地，大部分出口的咖啡豆會通過[[蘇伊士運河|蘇伊士運河]]運輸<ref name=value/>。

== 生長環境 ==
[[File:Coffee_Plantation1.jpg|缩略图]]
=== 氣候 ===
咖啡豆生長最理想的氣候條件是溫度介於攝氏23至28度，降雨量在1.5至2.0米之間，雨季後亦要有2-3個月的旱季。寒冷的氣溫接近冰點條件不適合種植咖啡。印度南部的降雨量雖少於1米，但設有灌溉設施，溫度及[[相對濕度|相對濕度]]也有利於咖啡豆的生長<ref name=coffee>{{Cite web|url=http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/124337/coffee|title=Coffee Production|accessdate=2010-10-05|publisher=Encyclopædia Britannica|archive-date=2010-04-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100429094019/http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/124337/coffee|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
=== 真菌侵蝕 ===
在印度，咖啡植物時常受到真菌影響。最常影響咖啡豆生長的真菌是{{link-en|''Hemileia vastatrix''|Hemileia vastatrix}}，目前仍未有根治的方法<ref name=archive>{{Cite web|url=http://www.archive.org/stream/encyclopediabrit06newyrich/encyclopediabrit06newyrich_djvu.txt|title= The Encyclopædia Britannica; a dictionary of arts, sciences, and general literature|work=Coffee|pages=110–112|accessdate=1 December 2010|author=Encyclopædia Britannica|publisher=Archive.org}}</ref>；咖啡植物亦會受到一種名為{{link-en|咖啡腐爛|Coffee rot}}的疾病影響，這種疾病在雨季會對咖啡植物造成嚴重的損害<ref name=archive />。

== 普及程度 ==
[[File:Happy_Valentine's_Day...!.jpg|缩略图]]{{link-en|咖啡日咖啡廳|Café Coffee Day}}提供的咖啡]]
印度第一所咖啡館於1957年10月27日在[[新德里|新德里]]，自此以後，印度全國各地漸漸出現連鎖的咖啡館<ref name=house>{{Cite web|url=http://www.hinduonnet.com/thehindu/mp/2002/09/23/stories/2002092300480100.htm|title=More than just coffee 'n snacks|accessdate=1 December 2010|publisher=The Hindu|date=23 September 2010|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090502032934/http://www.hinduonnet.com/thehindu/mp/2002/09/23/stories/2002092300480100.htm|archive-date=2009-05-02|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.indiancoffeehouse.com/abtus.htm|title=Indian coffee House|accessdate=1 December 2010|publisher=Indian Coffee House|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080724080620/http://www.indiancoffeehouse.com/abtus.htm|archivedate=2008年7月24日}}</ref>。今時今日，[[咖啡吧|咖啡吧]]（coffee bars）在印度愈趨普及，而{{link-en|咖啡日咖啡廳|Café Coffee Day}}是全國最大的連鎖咖啡吧<ref name="commodityonline">{{cite web|url=http://www.commodityonline.com/news/Cafe-Coffee-Day-bags-8-awards-at-India-Barista-15824-3-1.html|title=Cafe Coffee Day bags 8 awards at India Barista|date=7 March 2009|work=commodityonline.com|accessdate=1 December 2010|archive-date=2011-07-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110722190133/http://www.commodityonline.com/news/Cafe-Coffee-Day-bags-8-awards-at-India-Barista-15824-3-1.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。和栽種咖啡豆一樣，印度南部的咖啡消費量比其他地區較大<ref name="Majumdar">{{cite book|last=Majumdar|first=Ramanuj|title=Consumer Behaviour: Insights From Indian Market|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=KF57x1Nrn2UC&pg=RA2-PA279|year=2010|publisher=PHI Learning Pvt. Ltd.|isbn=81-203-3963-0|page=279|access-date=2014-07-08|archive-date=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140708114210/http://books.google.com/books?id=KF57x1Nrn2UC&pg=RA2-PA279|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 管理 ==
印度的咖啡產業是由{{link-en|印度工業和商業部|Ministry of Commerce and Industry (India)}}屬下的[[印度咖啡委員會|印度咖啡委員會]]（Coffee Board of India）管理<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.indiacoffee.org/indiacoffee.php?page=Aboutus |title=Coffee Board of India – About Us |first= |last= |work=indiacoffee.org |year=2011 |accessdate=22 October 2011 |archive-date=2008-12-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081225202544/http://www1.indiacoffee.org/indiacoffee.php?page=Aboutus |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。印度咖啡委員會負責推廣栽種咖啡、咖啡在國內外的銷售、進行有關咖啡研究、向小型[[咖啡農|咖啡農]]提供財政援助、保障咖啡農工作時的待遇和未能出售的咖啡<ref>{{cite book |title=Traditional Exports of India: Performance and Prospects |last=John |first=K. C. |author2=Kevin, S |year=2004 |publisher=New Century Publications |location=Delhi |isbn=81-7708-062-8 |page=117}}</ref>。

